    • Method Detail

      • visit

        public void visit(MysqlDatabase node)
        Sets values to default values that are not required by the EffectiveModel but by CloudFormation.
        Passwords need to have a length of 8. If it is shorter than that or no password is given at all, a random password is used instead.
        Compute nodes that only host MysqlDatabase should not be transformed to EC2s because the MysqlDatabase will be an AWS RDS and won't need a host.
        Specified by:
        visit in interface NodeVisitor
        Parameters:
        node - the MysqlDatabase node to visit
